{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"33ef710575","title":"对陶铸关于广东召开公社代表大会部署的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"59c635d010","index":0,"year":1959,"month":4,"day":20,"articleId":"33ef710575"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dbcf15bd08","name":"陶铸","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji41":{"comments":[{"id":"9bc4e328f2","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"33ef710575","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共广东省委第一书记陶铸1959年4月18日给毛泽东的这一报告说，从上海开会回来后，即按照指示布置全省各公社召开一次代表大会。接到主席在杭州的指示后，省委决定进一步加快进度，已通知各地、县，要各县立即召开一个社的代表大会，地委派人帮助，县委亲自掌握。省委在潮安搞的公社代表大会试点，已提前进行。5月初省委在潮安召开地委书记现场会议，交流经验，为全省全面铺开、分批召开公社代表大会作好准备。"},{"id":"c37c3a7390","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"33ef710575","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c05bc38547","type":"title","text":"对陶铸关于广东召开公社代表大会部署的报告\"的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"33ef710575"},{"id":"9bc4e328f2","type":"paragraph","text":"尚昆P","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"33ef710575"},{"id":"c37c3a7390","type":"paragraph","text":"请以电话告陶铸，赞成他的意见","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"33ef710575"},{"id":"9560dfb3a7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"33ef710575"},{"id":"bbc6776f08","type":"paragraph","text":"四月廿日上午二时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"33ef710575"}],"page":{"id":"2a4f958ddd","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"33ef710575","start":457,"end":457}}}},"__N_SSG":true}